@match help|Help|master
I would not suggest trying to slay my master! He is very strong and his castle is filled with dangerous vampires and undead. He himself used to be a dark elf, but became a lich. He has many powers and he also found an ancient scroll contained a powerful spell of madness. He has been using it on the dwarven miners.
@match spell|scroll|ancient scroll
You must get it away from him. If he uses it on you, you will become insane for life. You must destroy the scroll!
endmsg
